    "title": "Israel and Lebanon agree to 10-day ceasefire in push for permanent peace deal",
    "description": "BEIRUT: Israel and Lebanon agreed to a 10-day ceasefire on Thursday, Donald Trump said, with the US hoping the truce will lead to a permanent peace deal. The truce took effect at 2100 GMT on Thursday and Trump said he expected Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanhyahu and Lebanese President Joseph Aoun to visit the White House for direct talks in the next \"four or five days.\"",
